description:
Arkham Adventures, is set in a Post-Apocalyptic, Totalitarian world where the evil Roth's Corp., has taken control. The one's who go willingly are implanted with Nano-Technology that hijacks their consciousness, and turns them into a Human Robot. The one's who refused went underground to a cavern system known as WanderLost, and formed the Resistance. A newfound hope is found when it's revealed that someone has figured out a way to shutdown the 'Universal Nano-Bot Network' (UBNN), and destroy Roth's Corp.

Will they destroy it before, Roth's Corp., finds WanderLost?

Each image comes with a Diary Entry from one of three protagonists trying to navigate the treacherous land that once was Arkham.

All these photo's were taken while we were actually exploring various abandoned hospitals across America.
